{"tid":637013,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事麻煩廣傳) 垃圾電競主播買分實錄","createTime":"2018-04-21T12:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T00:53:02.000Z","uid":147066,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdc2e0e46228fc1a89d464181941d3acd7d2119","tid":637013,"uid":147066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/174332_159ac461dd1072159f64758f6d23837a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F174332_159ac461dd1072159f64758f6d23837a.jpg&h=92d8cd14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日我哋講呢位主角就係張圖上面箭咀指住嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一位買分仔好出色㗎<br />\n曾經做過大專盃2017初賽嘅賽評<br />\n仲要啱啱21號先又有份講咩咩咩英雄聯盟青年電競比賽2018<br />\n你條智障仔為咗做電競買ac  仲要出嚟同人講我係白金  笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你買咗個ac都冇用   最後自己輸返曬衣間變銀牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要畀佢本身玩嗰個低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/175608_95aa7de9aa2250b1de96bf878cc801be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F175608_95aa7de9aa2250b1de96bf878cc801be.jpg&h=acb76952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買分嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/175718_56650e220cb4a5ac8573e8a1c91eb977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F175718_56650e220cb4a5ac8573e8a1c91eb977.jpg&h=405cd99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身都已經有其他人起facebook踢爆佢  但係最後俾FB block咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下開放所有證據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/181459_4650993e72aefff86c827051751e06f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F181459_4650993e72aefff86c827051751e06f5.jpg&h=90a564df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/181225_25dcb5f81cf0e80e86b18c5de298db0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F181225_25dcb5f81cf0e80e86b18c5de298db0a.jpg&h=49b5e08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/181225_1d90b47d23d2d548d34d52f1f8bcc04f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F181225_1d90b47d23d2d548d34d52f1f8bcc04f.jpg&h=209c8db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180335_50fc700e49c6c94ca292fc1b4e843e90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180335_50fc700e49c6c94ca292fc1b4e843e90.jpg&h=24efc95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180335_1e0aaab435f615ab22665d4a498f9e93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180335_1e0aaab435f615ab22665d4a498f9e93.jpg&h=d2c6e6fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180336_a30a5a624cda6d7d36ebe635e8618117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180336_a30a5a624cda6d7d36ebe635e8618117.jpg&h=c318a81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180336_bce4ce294c3d2a75648b4c7ae591749f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180336_bce4ce294c3d2a75648b4c7ae591749f.jpg&h=3812b91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http